Deprecated API

Contents

Deprecated Methods
javassist.util.proxy.ProxyFactory.setHandler(MethodHandler)
          since 3.12 use of this method is incompatible with proxy class caching. instead clients should call method ProxyObject.setHandler(MethodHandler) to set the handler for each newly created proxy instance. calling this method will automatically disable caching of classes created by the proxy factory. 
javassist.CtClass.toClass(ClassLoader)
          Replaced by CtClass.toClass(ClassLoader,ProtectionDomain) 
javassist.ClassPool.toClass(CtClass, ClassLoader)
          Replaced by ClassPool.toClass(CtClass,ClassLoader,ProtectionDomain). A subclass of ClassPool that has been overriding this method should be modified. It should override ClassPool.toClass(CtClass,ClassLoader,ProtectionDomain).
